  m_text: 'Find the keys to open the exit gate, before the ghost steals your soul!


    The
    lantern can flash the ghost, but you need an Orb.


    Special goggles let you
    see through walls, but their use is limited.

    Wear and activate them by pressing
    the trigger button near to your head.'
